8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: start; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">记者采访了解到，行业的痛点主要聚焦在结构、组织和从业人员方面，这也是有关部门的工作发力点。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: start; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">余兴源介绍，在破局结构痛点方面，近年来，交通运输部会同相关部门采取“两点一线”作战——</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: start; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">以车型标准化为切入点，全面淘汰不合规车辆运输车3.2万辆，新增7万辆标准的车辆运输车进入市场并成为主力，同时，发布营运货车安全技术条件等行业标准;</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: start; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">以运输结构调整为重点，明确重点推进大宗货物中长途运输“公转铁、公转水”，运输结构调整成效初显;</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: start; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">打通城乡配送一条线，支持具有共同配送功能的枢纽园区建设，对新能源城市配送车辆给予便利通行，降低物流“最后一公里”成本。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages\" data-ratio=\"0.54765625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/qsgklf51MMBJibsREbYUvplnkKqGBAmmFgBo99O2qus6teftkp4TN3SmLHg12J9qkzYqrLYMVf1fpanWicmJvq9Q/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 677px !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: start; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">“跟结构痛点比起来，组织痛点更直观：司机找货难、运输效率不高。破局组织痛点，需要更强有力的抓手，要能在短期内产生效果。”余兴源说。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: start; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">“人在路上，家在车上。”余兴源说，为了让货车司机在路上时刻都有家的感觉，正在大力推进建设“司机之家”，目前已在全国建成并投入运营182个“司机之家”。如今，很多货车司机沿途都能“喝口热水、吃口热饭、洗个热水澡、睡个安稳觉”了。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages\" data-ratio=\"0.66640625\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"jpeg\" data-w=\"1280\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/qsgklf51MMAOPqgmaQ619eEXF44lMz8zRIdT63nLqJYyEFoe0QnjsB19CiatJuicJGLNwuK6oGAHxAOupQravGQw/640?wx_fmt=jpeg\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 677px !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: start; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">　　<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: start; color: rgb(123, 12, 0); font-size: 18px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">未来工作怎么干?</strong></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: start; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">上世纪80年代，货车司机走南闯北，报酬丰厚。“<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">方向盘一转，给个县长也不换”</strong>。路遥所著小说《平凡的世界》曾这样描述。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: start; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">在这之后，购买卡车的人越来越多，加上油价攀升，司机收入愈发不稳定。由于长年在车上久坐，缺乏锻炼，很多司机患有脊椎病、胃病等。时至今日，这些问题如同烙印，依然困扰着货车司机，制约着行业转型升级。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: start; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">“在推进道路货物运输高质量发展同时，要让货车司机有实实在在的获得感。”余兴源说。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><img class=\"rich_pages\" data-ratio=\"0.6577181208053692\" data-s=\"300,640\" data-type=\"png\" data-w=\"1341\" src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_png/qsgklf51MMDeIgibl0Bicm6gOWVJhjXClRvaXPDZVSgcjOddR8e76P4iaqscNfLHLsIsETgNMD9Yicpm7iaGiah06Omw/640?wx_fmt=png\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; height: auto !important; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important; visibility: visible !important; width: 677px !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: start; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">余兴源说，推进货运业转型发展的道路任重道远，未来将重点做好以下几方面工作：</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: start; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">持续推进货运车型标准化，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; text-align: start; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">加大力度推动运输结构调整，</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; text-align: start; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">全面提升货物运输组织化水平。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; text-align: start; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">努力办好“司机之家”民生实事，重点依托高速公路服务区、国省干线服务区、加油站、物流园区等，推进“司机</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; font-size: 15px; text-align: start; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">之家”建设。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px 8px; padding: 0px; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-size: 17px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: start; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">“在这条向着美好生活的道路上，货车司机在努力奔跑之时，我们也要真抓实干，让这条道路更加平坦宽阔。”余兴源说。</span></section><p></p><div><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(68, 68, 68); font-family: 微软雅黑; text-align: start; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br/></span></div><p><br/></p>',179,134,15,1600306585,1),(132,'统筹十问十答','new-17-729','5f62c0a4cec37.jpg','','','<p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:48px;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\"><span>1、<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">统筹是什么？</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:48px;text-indent:0;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family: &#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">它是一项针对交通运输这种高风险的行业特点，为确保交通运输系统各参统单位安全生产而产生的，具有行业互助性质的保障措施，具有明显的社会公益性。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:48px;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\"><span>2、<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">统筹是合规的吗？<span><span>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span></p><p style=\"margin-left:48px;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">交通安全统筹作为一个新事物出现，肯定有国家的相关文件支持，国务院关于加强道路交通安全工作的意见（国发【<span>2012</span>】<span>30</span>号），以及河北省人民政府关于进一步加强道路交通安全工作的实施意见（冀政【<span>2013</span>】<span>4</span>号）都明确指出，鼓励运输企业采用交通安全统筹等形式，加强行业互助，提高企业抗风险能力。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:48px;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\"><span>3、<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">统筹的理赔靠谱吗？跟保险公司有什么区别吗？</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:48px;text-indent:0;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family: &#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">统筹是个老话题，新事物，以前内部统筹也有，但大部分没有发展起来，追其原因主要是统户少，补偿金薄弱，抗风险能力不足。统户信心受到影响，参统意念逐渐凋零，导致统筹工作难以为继。针对市场需求及较之前的内部统筹的短板，中互交通于<span>2019.7</span>月注册资金<span>1</span>亿<span>,</span>经市场监管局审批<span>,</span>市场审批局批准获得了交通安全统筹开展行业互助的资格<span>.</span>抗风险准备金<span>2000</span>万<span>,</span>确保统户安全生产<span>,</span>统筹赔偿金落到实处<span>. </span>其次打造专业团队<span>,</span>健全安全制度<span>,</span>让专业的人干专业的事<span>.</span>我们成立之初先后聘请了保险公司的行业专家精英<span>,</span>建立组织架构形成专业管理团队<span>,</span>用专业的团队管理机制及服务来吸引有需求的运输企业加入我们的会员<span>,</span>真正做到一方有难<span>,</span>八方支援的愿望<span>.</span>科学严谨的安全制度是做好工作的重要保障<span>,</span>确保公司更顺畅的开展公司建立了更多的科学制度<span>;1,</span>交通安全管理<span>,2,</span>财务管理<span>,3,</span>业务发展<span>,4,</span>现场救援<span>,5,</span>事故理赔的统一调剂<span>,</span>公司在制度上的创新不断的在摸索前进<span>,</span>针对统户的【安全统筹的十问十答<span>)</span>】【交通安全统筹承统操作指南】<span>,</span>【交通事故经济补偿的工作流程】<span>,</span>【补偿金的管理规定】机制<span>.</span>【交通运输企业安全管理的培训制度】。<span><br/> </span>统筹与保险公司的区别在性质不同；保险公司是商业行为，注重利益的最大化。统筹是行政行为，具有互帮互助的功能，具有明显的公益性。管理机关不同，保险根据保险法受银保监会监管。统筹是由政府职能部门及交通运输厅监管。服务理念不同；保险强调的是为所有的客户服务，注重的是经济效益。统筹服务的主体是交通运输企业，注重的是安全管理，预防为主，具有补偿特色功能。责任范围不同；保险按合同赔付，追求经济效益。统筹是以安全管理相结合，能主动防范降低事故率，安全促生产，提高企业的抗风险能力。在重大案件及困难统户出险后给予适当的额外补偿，更具人性化。发展方向不同；保险的发展方向是让所有的人得到安全保障，有合同条款为基础，得到保障功能。统筹的发展方向；降低运输企业风险事故率，安全管理，安全教育，提高运输企业的生产效率，减少运输企业的运营成本，提高企业核心竞争力。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:48px;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\"><span>4、<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">今年入的统筹明年在入保险公司是不是就没有去年记录了？</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:48px;text-indent:0;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family: &#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">同样分两点说明，第一如果车在本年度发生过理赔案件，无论一次还是两次，最终如果客户满意，他不会反而去选择保险公司投保的，如果不满意，车辆出险记录保险公司不会体现，车辆可以按照断保<span>6</span>个月以上继续投保保险公司，折扣比出险后要合适很多 ；第二如果客户没出险，来年想选择保险公司，同样是断保<span>6</span>月以上投保，你上年度投保的统筹单，已经为客户省下来一笔钱了，就算来年在保险公司上，合计下来也是合适的。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:48px;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\"><span>5、<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">统筹受监管吗？</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:48px;text-indent:0;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family: &#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">交通统筹作为新的事物出现，需要一个发展过程，在这个发展过程中，有质疑是肯定的，保险行业一样是经过多年的发展不断的完善，才有今天的规模，我们目前已经跟市政府、省交通厅在协商洽谈，用我们已经拟稿的统筹大纲，来管理我们的统筹市场以及监督，并且我们现在是省交通厅交通运输协会的副会长单位，我们会向先进的省份学习，让政府或者交通厅来监管，这需要我们不断努力。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:48px;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\"><span>6、<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">保险公司是否认可统筹？</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:48px;text-indent:0;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family: &#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">统筹市场发展已经经历了很多年，目前各保险公司均认可我们的统筹单了 ，在我公司参统车辆，三者承保<span>100</span>万，便可以在保险公司投保超赔险，以及一些贷款金融机构，也有一部分同样认同了我们的统筹单。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:48px;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\"><span>7、<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">如果客户不认可要退统能退吗？</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:48px;text-indent:0;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family: &#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">所有的客户都是自主参统，如果中间有任何疑虑或者退统，均是可以的，并且手续比保险公司方便快捷的多。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:48px;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\"><span>8、<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">统筹对比保险的优势在哪里？</span></p><p style=\"text-indent:24px;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family: &#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">统筹的创新的发展模式，让统筹服务多元化。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:48px;text-indent:0;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height: 115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">，建立驾驶人培训中心。相关数据显示，交通运输企业事故率高其一是新手经验不知，其二是疲劳驾驶，为了解决两大顽疾，创立驾驶人培训中心，以安全管理，安全教育，驾驶人的专业素质全方位的培训，从根本上降低运输企业的风险事故率，提高企业抗风险能力。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:48px;text-indent:0;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height: 115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">，对伤亡，残疾统户，给予公益扶持，对直系亲属，上学，工作，生活困难的家庭给予人文关怀，真正做到互助统筹的特色，</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:48px;text-indent:0;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height: 115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">，成立事故统筹委员会。统筹中心客户服务部与参统单位密切联系，做到提前介入送医救治，心里干预，经济扶持，一对一专业服务，不拼单，不共享服务，最大限度的降低统户的心里负担和精神痛苦。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:48px;text-indent:0;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height: 115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">，建立交通安全管理平台，物联网结合，减轻驾驶人心里压力。中国<span>70%</span>以上是公路运输，随着互联网快速发展，运输企业发展迅速的同时竞争压力愈演愈烈，低价格竞争导致运输企业拉快活，多趟次，抢时间来弥补运输成本的增加，导致运输企业驾驶人心里压力过大，风险递增，事故频发。针对这种情况，我们建立安全管理平台，针对第二年的参统高风险车辆免费安装物联网车载软件，实行后台人，车时时监控，减轻驾驶人心里压力，提高企业工作效率，预防为主，有效提高运输企业事故发生率确保道路安全良性发展。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:48px;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\"><span>9、<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">统筹理赔案例分析</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:48px;text-indent:0;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family: &#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">我司承保的一辆<span>10</span>吨以上货车 ，在正常行驶的情况下，与一辆拐弯经过的摩托车相撞，未造成重大伤亡，但摩托车司机住院检查，在第一次办理住院的时候，摩托车司机的家属表示出了很强烈的不满以及不友好的态度，但是我公司理赔员在伤者住院以后，每天都会去慰问伤者，探望时间每次不低于<span>30</span>分钟，经过<span>7</span>天的连续探望沟通，伤者出院后很配合的在理赔材料上签字了 ，而理赔款也在伤者提供全资料以后的第二天赔付了。为此，司机师傅亲自来我司送的锦旗，标明了：快速理赔，服务周到。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:48px;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\"><span>10、<span style=\"font:9px &#39;Times New Roman&#39;\">&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp; </span></span></span><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">统筹总结</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-left:48px;text-indent:0;line-height:115%\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;line-height:115%;font-family: &#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">发展信念<span>,</span>排除不利因素<span>,</span>维护运输企业的自身利益<span>;</span>交通安全统筹即时老话题又是新事物<span>,</span>曾经出现过很多运输企业的内保即是互助统筹的初级模式<span>,</span>有些人存在疑虑持怀疑态度片面的认为安全统筹没有生命力<span>,</span>更是认为是被淘汰的组织<span>.2012</span>国务院办公厅就关于道路安全下发鼓励交通运输企业以交通安全统筹的方式互帮互助<span>,</span>提高企业抗风险能力<span>,</span>这是进一步改革发展的趋势<span>,</span>顺应市场<span>,</span>顺应需求<span>,</span>这是给与我们不断探索或得成功的因数<span>,</span>有需求就有市场<span>,</span>我们建立了一个以商业保险外的交通安全管理为主题的预防为主的安全管保障模式<span>.</span></span></p><p><br/></p>',177,134,14,1600307364,1),(133,'中互交通运输有限公司简介','new-50-656','5f62c18da1927.jpg','','','<p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">一、安全统筹介绍</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">安全统筹是一项针对交通运输企业高风险的行业特点，为确保交通运输系统各参统单位安全生产而产生的，具有行业互助性质的保障措施，具有明显的社会公益性。交通安全统筹工作始终贯穿于参统单位安全管理机制的全过程，既坚持“安全第一，预防为主”的方针，切实加强安全监督，不断加大安全设施的投入，又注重事故发生后的善后处理，确保社会稳定，“安全保统筹，统筹促安全”最终达到促进道路安全发展的目的。<span><br style=\"text-align: left;\"/> <br style=\"text-align: left;\"/> </span><strong>二、统筹公司与保险公司有什么区别呢？</strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">答：</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">咱们从两点来说明，第一国家扶持统筹的出现就是为了解决现下保险公司所不能解决的难题、痛点而出现的，因为大货车在出险以后，到最终理赔结束，保险公司经过多个环节的处理，往往会造成时效低下，车在停车场放很长时间，而往往大货车就是靠上路拉货挣钱谋生，车多停一天就多损失一天，客户满意度非常低，只不过大家都认为保险公司靠谱，实在不行以后我可以起诉来做到理赔，但是根本就没从本质上解决问题；作为统筹而言，事故出险后直接拨打报案电话</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">400-681-8811</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">，都是由专人负责整个理赔环节，无需客户来往于第三方与公司之间，并且与第三方沟通事宜均由我司理赔员来处理解决，做到替客户着想，替企业分忧，全国均可以勘查理赔，用客户自己的话说 ，就算最后你觉得不合适，一样可以用对待保险公司的方式解决，起诉。因为我们的统筹单上的解决纷争方式是【诉讼】，但是我们做统筹，到目前为止，一个起诉案件都没发生，也变相的</span><span style=\"font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; font-size: 16px;\">说明了问题。另外我们有很多案例可以分享给您，如果您有需要的话可以来我们公司视察，我们公司是完全开放性的公司为了得到广大客户的认可，我们非常期望客户成为我们的监督者。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">三、统筹的优势在哪里？</span></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">统筹的创新的发展模式，让统筹服务多元化。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">，建立驾驶人培训中心。相关数据显示，交通运输企业事故率高其一是新手经验不知，其二是疲劳驾驶，为了解决两大顽疾，创立驾驶人培训中心，以安全管理，安全教育，驾驶人的专业素质全方位的培训，从根本上降低运输企业的风险事故率，提高企业抗风险能力。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">，对伤亡，残疾统户，给予公益扶持，对直系亲属，上学，工作，生活困难的家庭给予人文关怀，真正做到互助统筹的特色，</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">，成立事故统筹委员会。统筹中心客户服务部与参统单位密切联系，做到提前介入送医救治，心里干预，经济扶持，一对一专业服务，不拼单，不共享服务，最大限度的降低统户的心里负担和精神痛苦。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">，建立交通安全管理平台，物联网结合，减轻驾驶人心里压力。中国<span>70%</span>以上是公路运输，随着互联网快速发展，运输企业发展迅速的同时竞争压力愈演愈烈，低价格竞争导致运输企业拉快活，多趟次，抢时间来弥补运输成本的增加，导致运输企业驾驶人心里压力过大，风险递增，事故频发。针对这种情况，我们建立安全管理平台，针对第二年的参统高风险车辆免费安装物联网车载软件，实行后台人，车时时监控，减轻驾驶人心里压力，提高企业工作效率，预防为主，有效提高运输企业事故发生率确保道路安全良性发展。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;;color:black\">四、</span><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family: &#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">客服部服务承诺</span></strong><strong></strong></p><p style=\"text-align:center\"></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">客户出险</span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"http://test2.ericgu178.com/Uploads/image/20200917/1600308208602874.png\" title=\"1600308208602874.png\" _src=\"/Uploads/image/20200917/1600308208602874.png\" alt=\"image.png\" width=\"61\" height=\"19\" style=\"width: 61px; height: 19px;\"/></span></strong><strong style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family: &#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">报案受理<strong style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><img src=\"http://test2.ericgu178.com/Uploads/image/20200917/1600308208602874.png\" title=\"1600308208602874.png\" _src=\"/Uploads/image/20200917/1600308208602874.png\" alt=\"image.png\" width=\"61\" height=\"19\" style=\"width: 61px; height: 19px;\"/></span></strong></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">查勘定损<strong style=\"white-space: normal; text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong><img src=\"http://test2.ericgu178.com/Uploads/image/20200917/1600308208602874.png\" title=\"1600308208602874.png\" _src=\"/Uploads/image/20200917/1600308208602874.png\" alt=\"image.png\" width=\"61\" height=\"19\" style=\"width: 61px; height: 19px;\"/></strong></span></strong></span></strong><strong style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family: &#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">提交理赔资料<strong style=\"white-space: normal;\"><span style=\"font-size: 16px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;\"><strong style=\"text-align: center;\"><strong><img src=\"http://test2.ericgu178.com/Uploads/image/20200917/1600308208602874.png\" title=\"1600308208602874.png\" _src=\"/Uploads/image/20200917/1600308208602874.png\" alt=\"image.png\" width=\"61\" height=\"19\" style=\"width: 61px; height: 19px;\"/></strong></strong></span></strong></span></strong><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">补偿打款</span></strong></p><p><strong></strong></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">报案理赔须知：</span></strong><br/></p><p style=\"text-indent: 32px; text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">为实现公司实施统一化管理，凡是参加交通安全统筹的参统户，如有报案、咨询、查询、投诉等需要，可随时拨打<span>24</span>小时全国统一客服热线：<span>400-681-8811</span>。中互交通客服部也会在接到热线后，第一时间统一派发案件，做到案件管理的统一性和及时性，主要承诺如下：</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">、报案电话专员：来电响铃，三声内接听。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">、客服查勘专员：接到指令，立即联系。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">各项手续资料齐全，结案完毕后。</span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">1</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">、万元（含）以内赔款，<span>24</span>小时内汇出； </span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">2</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">、<span>1-10</span>万元（含）赔款，<span>48</span>小时内汇出； </span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">3</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">、<span>10</span>万<span>-50</span>万元（含）赔款，三个工作日内汇出； </span></p><p style=\"text-align: left;\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">4</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">、<span>50</span>万<span>-100</span>万元（含）赔款，五个工作日内汇出； </span></p><p style=\"margin-left: 131px; text-indent: 64px; text-align: left;\"><strong><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">监督投诉电话：<span>400-681-8811</span></span></strong></p><p><br style=\"text-align: left;\"/></p>',180,134,13,1600307597,1),(134,'