\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">超限具体罚多少，在《超限运输车辆行驶公路管理规定》也有明确规定。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"2185\" data-color=\"#1e9be8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><section data-color=\"#1e9be8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 27px; padding: 5px 10px 0px 35px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: inherit; font-size: 16px; border-left: 2px dotted rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><section data-original-title=\"\" title=\"\" style=\"margin: 23px 0px 0px -53px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 32px; height: 32px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; border-radius: 16px; background: rgb(30, 155, 232);\">1</section><section style=\"margin: -30px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: inherit;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">车货总高度从地面算起未超过4.2米、总宽度未超过3米且总长度未超过20米的，可以处200元以下罚款；</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">车货总高度从地面算起未超过4.5米、总宽度未超过3.75米且总长度未超过28米的，处200元以上1000元以下罚款；</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">车货总高度从地面算起超过4.5米、总宽度超过3.75米或者总长度超过28米的，处1000元以上3000元以下的罚款。</span></section></section></section></section></section></section><section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"2185\" data-color=\"#1e9be8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0.5em; max-width: 100%; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><section data-color=\"#1e9be8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 27px; padding: 5px 10px 0px 35px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: inherit; font-size: 16px; border-left: 2px dotted rgb(228, 228, 228);\"><section data-original-title=\"\" title=\"\" data-num=\"2\" style=\"margin: 23px 0px 0px -53px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 32px; height: 32px; color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-align: center; line-height: 32px; border-radius: 16px; background: rgb(30, 155, 232);\">2</section><section style=\"margin: -30px 0px 0px; padding: 0px 0px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; color: inherit;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">车货总质量超限但未超过1000千克的，予以警告；超过1000千克的，每超1000千克罚款500元，最高不得超过30000元。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">有前款所列多项违法行为的，相应违法行为的罚款数额应当累计，但累计罚款数额最高不得超过30000元。</span></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section data-support=\"96编辑器\" data-style-id=\"17526\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section data-support=\"96编辑器\" data-style-id=\"17526\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section data-role=\"paragraph\" data-color=\"#1e9be8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"88109\" data-color=\"#1e9be8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; text-align: center; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 5px 20px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-radius: 4px; border-width: 1px; border-style: solid; border-color: rgb(30, 155, 232); display: inline-block; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(77, 168, 238); box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp;运管的处罚标准：</strong></span></p></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">运管执法的根据是《道路运输条例》，其中规定，运输货物的车辆不得运客，并严禁超载；载物的长、宽、高不得违反装载要求。若违反规定的，由公安交管部门依照《道路交通安全法》进行处罚。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">也就是说，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">运管在遇到货车超限运输时，不能直接对其进行处罚，而应该由交警进行处罚。</strong></span></section><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p><br/></p><p></p>',179,134,12,1600308749,1),(135,'转载》国务院关于加强道路交通安全工作的意见国发（2012）30号文件','new-72-798','5f641516a6eea.jpg','转载》国务院关于加强道路交通安全工作的意见国发（2012）30号文件','转载》国务院关于加强道路交通安全工作的意见国发（2012）30号文件','<p style=\"margin-top: auto; margin-bottom: auto; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\" microsoft=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">转载》国务院关于加强道路交通安全工作的意见国发（</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;\">2012</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">）</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif; color: black;\">30</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体; color: black;\">号文件</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;\"></strong></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 10px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, \" microsoft=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-indent:=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, \" microsoft=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">各省、自治区、直辖市人民政府，国务院各部委、各直属机构：</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;\"/></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">　　为适应我国道路通车里程、机动车和驾驶人数量、道路交通运量持续大幅度增长的形势，进一步加强道路交通安全工作，保障人民群众生命财产安全，提出以下意见：</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;\"/></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">　　一、总体要求</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;\"/></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">　　（一）指导思想。以邓小平理论和</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">“</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">三个代表</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">”</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">重要思想为指导，深入贯彻落实科学发展观，牢固树立以人为本、安全发展的理念，始终把维护人民群众生命财产安全放在首位，以防事故、保安全、保畅通为核心，以落实企业主体责任为重点，全面加强人、车、路、环境的安全管理和监督执法，推进交通安全社会管理创新，形成政府统一领导、各部门协调联动、全社会共同参与的交通安全管理工作格局，有效防范和坚决遏制重特大道路交通事故，促进全国安全生产形势持续稳定好转，为经济社会发展、人民平安出行创造良好环境。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;\"/></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">　　（二）基本原则。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;\"/></span>　　<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">——</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">安全第一，协调发展。正确处理安全与速度、质量、效益的关系，坚持把安全放在首位，加强统筹规划，使道路交通安全融入国民经济社会发展大局，与经济社会同步协调发展。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;\"/></span>　　<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">——</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">预防为主，综合治理。严格驾驶人、车辆、运输企业准入和安全管理，加强道路交通安全设施建设，深化隐患排查治理，着力解决制约和影响道路交通安全的源头性、根本性问题，夯实道路交通安全基础。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;\"/></span>　　<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">——</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">落实责任，强化考核。全面落实企业主体责任、政府及部门监管责任和属地管理责任，健全目标考核和责任追究制度，加强督导检查和责任倒查，依法严格追究事故责任。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;\"/></span>　　<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\">——</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">科技支撑，法治保障。强化科技装备和信息化技术应用，建立健全法律法规和标准规范，加强执法队伍建设，依法严厉打击各类交通违法违规行为，不断提高道路交通科学管理与执法服务水平。</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;\"/></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">　　二、强化道路运输企业安全管理</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: Arial, sans-serif;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;\"/></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; font-size: 16px; font-family: 宋体;\">　　（三）规范道路运输企业生产经营行为。严格道路运输市场准入管理，对新设立运输企业，要严把安全管理制度和安全生产条件审核关。强化道路运输企业安全主体责任，鼓励客运企业实行规模化、公司化经营，积极培育集约化、网络化经营的货运龙头企业。严禁客运车辆、危险品运输车辆挂靠经营。推进道路运输企业诚信体系建设，将诚信考核结果与客运线路招投标、运力投放以及保险费率、银行信贷等挂钩，不断完善企业安全管理的激励约束机制。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; background: silver;\">鼓励运输企业采用交通安全统筹等形式，加强行业互助，提高企业抗风险能力。</span></strong></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: right;\" microsoft=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" font-size:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\"><span style=\"text-align: right;\">----------------节选</span></p><p><br/></p>',174,123,11,1600311383,0),(141,'为什么你的轴承润滑会变硬？','new-63-248','5f64173047951.jpg','为什么你的轴承润滑脂会变硬？','相信不少车友遇到过轴承润滑脂在运转中有发干变硬的现象，润滑脂变硬后，就会造成阻塞，导致系统润滑不良，增大机械部件摩擦阻力、增加机械动力的消耗等。那么，轴承润滑脂为什么会变硬呢？\r\n\r\n','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" ya