 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;\">轴承加注的润滑脂过多、机械条件引发的过热（安装不当、负载过重等等）、润滑不足都可能引起运行中的过热问题，其中，加注的润滑脂过多是一个常见诱因。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;\">如果车辆在运行过程中机械温度过高，达到了润滑脂的滴点，基础油就会开始析出，从而导致润滑脂开始变干发硬。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><img src=\"/Uploads/image/20200918/1600394632211044.png\" title=\"1600394632211044.png\" _src=\"/Uploads/image/20200918/1600394632211044.png\" alt=\"image.png\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;\">因此，车友们在进行轴承润滑保养时，不要认为润滑脂加的越多越好，适量的才是最好的。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p></p><section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"92290\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><section data-width=\"100%\" style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 677px; text-align: center;\"><section data-num=\"3\" style=\"margin: 0px auto; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; width: 45px; height: 45px; font-weight: bold; line-height: 50px; font-size: 20px;\">3</section></section></section><p></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px; font-family: 黑体, SimHei;\">半径大、速度高的轴承会产生很高的离心力，也可以使得润滑脂分油，从而导致润滑脂硬化。</span></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; colo