-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(77, 168, 238); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"></span></strong></span><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></h2></section></section></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">很多卡车起火是因为电器线路起火，线路起火的的原因有哪些呢？</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><img src=\"/Uploads/image/20200917/1600313494652092.png\" title=\"1600313494652092.png\" _src=\"/Uploads/image/20200917/1600313494652092.png\" alt=\"blob.png\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">一是用电量大，线路的负荷大生热自燃；</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">二是由于线路老化、线路破损，会导致线路与车体搭铁（短路）出现线路过热、产生火花，从而引起线路起火进而殃及全车</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">。</span></strong></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">起火的线路一般位于</span>发动机<span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">周围，线路上多少会带有一些油迹，所以当线路过载发热出现火苗的时候，这些油迹会助燃将火情迅速扩大。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">发动机上的油迹很大一部分来自气门室盖、</strong></span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">机油</strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">滤芯、曲轴通风箱等部位，还有就是柴油管路渗漏的柴油。</span></strong></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"></span></strong></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></strong></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">解决方案：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">平时多加检查，看车辆的线路是否有干涩、磨损的地方，如有需要及时进行维修。</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">同时<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">检查各油路是否有漏油的地方，气门室罩盖、曲轴通风箱等部分是否有渗油的部位。</strong>如有，将发动机上的油迹进行清理，将渗油的地方进行维修，防患于未然。</span></section><p></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p></p><section data-color=\"#ef7060\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; font-family: Arial, \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; border-bottom: 1.5px solid rgb(0, 176, 240); border-top-color: rgb(0, 176, 240); border-right-color: rgb(0, 176, 240); border-left-color: rgb(0, 176, 240); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial; display: flex; justify-content: flex-start; align-items: flex-end; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section placeholder=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px 8px 0px 0px; padding: 4px 10px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-weight: bold; color: rgb(255, 255, 254); float: left; line-height: 20px; background-color: rgb(0, 176, 240); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">2<br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><h2 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; text-align: center; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(77, 168, 238);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 17px;\">轮毂、制动系统起火</span></strong></span></h2></section></section></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\"><img src=\"/Uploads/image/20200917/1600313531315169.png\" title=\"1600313531315169.png\" _src=\"/Uploads/image/20200917/1600313531315169.png\" alt=\"blob.png\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">由于</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">挂车</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">车轴引起的火灾也不在少数</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">，挂车轮毂没有做到及时保养是原因之一，内部的油脂减少或者变质，润滑条件变差会导致轮毂温度的升高，导致轮毂内的油脂起火，从而导致后部挂车起火殃及全车。除此之外，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">轮毂轴承间隙过大或过小、轴承走外缘、继动阀卡滞、总泵卡滞都能引起温度过高。</strong></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">除了挂车轮毂的原因，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">挂车刹车片的间隙过小、或者刹车突然抱死，长时间刹车制动也会导致刹车盔温度急剧升高</strong>，轮毂内的油脂因温度高会流到制动鼓内，引起火苗导致</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">轮胎</span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">起火，轮胎起火后会将车厢上的苫布、货物引燃。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">解决方案：</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><img src=\"/Uploads/image/20200917/1600313599926723.png\" title=\"1600313599926723.png\" _src=\"/Uploads/image/20200917/1600313599926723.png\" alt=\"blob.png\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">及时做好车辆的各项保养，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">尤其是轮毂与刹车这两个部位</strong>。同时加强车辆的日常检查，及时进行维修保养。车内配备灭火器，并掌握灭火器的正确操作方式，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">在日常需要查看灭火器的压力指针，发现压力过低需要进行更换。</strong></span></section><p></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p></p><section data-color=\"#ef7060\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; white-space: normal; font-family: Arial, \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; display: inline-block; border-bottom: 1.5px solid rgb(0, 176, 240); border-top-color: rgb(0, 176, 240); border-right-color: rgb(0, 176, 240); border-left-color: rgb(0, 176, 240); overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-col