nt; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section data-role=\"paragraph\" data-color=\"#1e9be8\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">夏日驾驶室内要是存放了<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">打火机、除锈剂、酒精等易燃易爆物品</strong>是一件非常危险的事情。这些易燃易爆物品在高温的驾驶室内极易引起自燃发生火灾。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><img src=\"/Uploads/image/20200917/1600314782758445.png\" title=\"1600314782758445.png\" _src=\"/Uploads/image/20200917/1600314782758445.png\" alt=\"blob.png\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">在夏天的时候为了防止蚊子的叮咬，司机会选择点燃蚊香来熏除蚊子，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">蚊香放置固定不好的话，蚊香掉落容易引燃其它物品。</strong></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">说完夏季高温容易引起火灾，我们来说说冬季的注意事项。在冬季我们在车内睡觉一般会选择车用电热毯进行取暖。电热毯如果质量不达标、电热毯长时间工作很容易引起火灾，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">所以在冬季使用电热毯的时候要多加注意，在离开车的时候将电热毯断电</strong>，防止意外的发生。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">除此之外，在冬季的时候我们也会使用</span><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">驻车加热器</span></strong><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">进行取暖，驻车加热的周围、出风口、尾气排放口在工作的时候温度很高，尤其是排气口温度能达到140多度，如果有易燃品，非常容易引起火灾。</span></strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></strong></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkM',179,134,9,1600314415,1),(138,'统筹对比保险的优势在哪里？','new-77-830','5f630149f2330.jpg','统筹的创新的发展模式，让统筹服务多元化。','统筹的创新的发展模式，让统筹服务多元化。\r\n\r\n1，建立驾驶人培训中心。相关数据显示，交通运输企业事故率高其一是新手经验不知，其二是疲劳驾驶，为了解决两大顽疾，创立驾驶人培训中心，以安全管理，安全教育，驾驶人的专业素质全方位的培训，从根本上降低运输企业的风险事故率，提高企业抗风险能力','<p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: arial, &quot;Microsoft Yahei&quot;, &quot;Hiragino Sans GB&quot;, sans-serif; font-size: 14px; white-space: normal; background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255); text-indent: 24px; line-height: 16.1px; text-align: center;\"><strong><span style=\"padding: 0px; transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s; line-height: 18.4px; font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif; color: black; font-size: 18px;\">统筹的创新的发展模式，让统筹服务多元化。</span></strong></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 48px;padding: 0px;transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: arial, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 16.1px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;font-size: 16px;line-height: 18.4px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;color: black\"><br/></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 48px;padding: 0px;transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: arial, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 16.1px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;font-size: 16px;line-height: 18.4px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;color: black\"><br/></span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 48px;padding: 0px;transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: arial, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 16.1px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;font-size: 16px;line-height: 18.4px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;color: black\"> &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;&nbsp;1</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;font-size: 16px;line-height: 18.4px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;color: black\">，建立驾驶人培训中心。相关数据显示，交通运输企业事故率高其一是新手经验不知，其二是疲劳驾驶，为了解决两大顽疾，创立驾驶人培训中心，以安全管理，安全教育，驾驶人的专业素质全方位的培训，从根本上降低运输企业的风险事故率，提高企业抗风险能力。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 48px;padding: 0px;transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: arial, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 16.1px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;font-size: 16px;line-height: 18.4px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;color: black\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;2</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;font-size: 16px;line-height: 18.4px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;color: black\">，对伤亡，残疾统户，给予公益扶持，对直系亲属，上学，工作，生活困难的家庭给予人文关怀，真正做到互助统筹的特色。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 48px;padding: 0px;transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: arial, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 16.1px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;font-size: 16px;line-height: 18.4px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;color: black\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;3</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;font-size: 16px;line-height: 18.4px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;color: black\">，成立事故统筹委员会。统筹中心客户服务部与参统单位密切联系，做到提前介入送医救治，心里干预，经济扶持，一对一专业服务，不拼单，不共享服务，最大限度的降低统户的心里负担和精神痛苦。</span></p><p class=\"MsoListParagraph\" style=\"margin-top: 0px;margin-bottom: 0px;margin-left: 48px;padding: 0px;transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;color: rgb(51, 51, 51);font-family: arial, &#39;Microsoft Yahei&#39;, &#39;Hiragino Sans GB&#39;, sans-serif;font-size: 14px;white-space: normal;background-color: rgb(255, 255, 255);line-height: 16.1px\"><span style=\";padding: 0px;transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;font-size: 16px;line-height: 18.4px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;color: black\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;4</span><span style=\";padding: 0px;transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s;font-size: 16px;line-height: 18.4px;font-family: 微软雅黑, sans-serif;color: black\">，建立交通安全管理平台，物联网结合，减轻驾驶人心里压力。中国<span style=\";padding: 0px;transition: background-color 0.4s ease 0s, opacity 0.4s ease 0s, border-color 0.2s ease 0s\">70%</span>以上是公路运输，随着互联网快速发展，运输企业发展迅速的同时竞争压力愈演愈烈，低价格竞争导致运输企业拉快活，多趟次，抢时间来弥补运输成本的增加，导致运输企业驾驶人心里压力过大，风险递增，事故频发。针对这种情况，我们建立安全管理平台，针对第二年的参统高风险车辆免费安装物联网车载软件，实行后台人，车时时监控，减轻驾驶人心里压力，提高企业工作效率，预防为主，有效提高运输企业事故发生率确保道路安全良性发展。</span></p><h1><br/></h1>',177,134,8,1600323848,0),(139,'货车超限被罚将纳入征信!已有超限者无法贷款','new-6-598','5f630339e50c9.jpeg','货车超限被罚将纳入征信!已有超限者无法贷款','货车超限被罚将纳入征信！已有超限者无法贷款\r\n       近日，福建厦门一物流公司到银行办理申请贷款等业务时，被告知因有条违法超限运输记录在案，公司必须出示相关已履行义务的证明材料，否则将无法继续进入贷款的下一步流程。','<h2 class=\"rich_media_title\" id=\"activity-name\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 14px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 22px; line-height: 1.4; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" text-align:=\"\"><strong>货车超限被罚将纳入征信！已有超限者无法贷款</strong></h2><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;近日，福建厦门一物流公司到银行办理<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">申请贷款</strong>等业务时，被告知<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">因有条违法超限运输记录在案</strong>，公司必须<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">出示相关已履行义务的证明材料</strong>，否则将无法继续进入贷款的下一步流程。</span></section><p></p><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; colo