r:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 据悉，该物流公司于2020年7月因<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">道路运输企业一年内违法超限运输车辆超过本单位货运车辆总数10%，被市交通执法支队责令停业整顿。</strong>由于需要提供已经履行义务的材料，该物流公司到厦门市交通运输综合执法支队申请征信证明。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section><section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"2446\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" color:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"2446\" data-color=\"#ef7060\" data-custom=\"#80b135\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px 8px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-radius: 3px; border-left: 3px solid rgb(84, 141, 212); border-top-color: rgb(84, 141, 212); border-right-color: rgb(84, 141, 212); border-bottom-color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-size: 22px; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;\"><h2 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(77, 168, 238); font-size: 20px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">超载将被纳入征信系统</strong></span></h2><h2 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(77, 168, 238); font-size: 17px;\">影响企业的征信</span></h2></section></section></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;随后，厦门市交通执法支队给所有的货运企业做出提醒——<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">违法超限运输不仅将面临公安部门以及交通运输部门的处罚，同时违法处罚的记录还将被纳入征信系统，今后可能影响企业的征信。</strong></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><img src=\"https://mmbiz.qpic.cn/mmbiz_jpg/faTiat0CmQgDr6XCQhaal0I0BMtDzDtibHUJn9fRoYKbh08X9VF6BNOHWE84Vok3nszIib8JgzkmZicM42BlFz8B3A/640?wx_fmt=jpeg&tp=webp&wxfrom=5&wx_lazy=1&wx_co=1\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;近些年，全国各地对超载超限车辆的违法行为纳入征信系统，定期将被处罚的车辆的所有单位、个人处罚信息推送至<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">“信用中国”平台</strong>，而这些违法记录也将对企业的生产活动产生影响，包括<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">上述企业贷款等，或许还会影响子女升学</strong>。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;据悉，失信当事人必须在规定期限内纠正失信行为、消除不良影响，进行信用修复，才能从“黑名单”中移出，按程序解除惩戒。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section><p></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.8); font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br/></p><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" color:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" display:=\"\" justify-content:=\"\" align-items:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><section data-brushtype=\"text\" style=\"margin: 0px 0px 0px 10px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0);\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(77, 168, 238);\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 18px;\">小编有话说</span></strong></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; flex: 1 1 0%; height: 1px; overflow: hidden; background-color: rgb(51, 51, 51);\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 1em; max-width: 100%; font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" color:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" font-size:=\"\" border-right:=\"\" 1px=\"\" solid=\"\" border-top-style:=\"\" border-bottom:=\"\" border-left:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" word-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><section data-autoskip=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 1em 0px 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 14px; letter-spacing: 1.5px; line-height: 1.75em;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 27.2px;\"><section data-autoskip=\"1\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 1em 0px 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em;\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; line-height: 1.75em; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 从该事件我们可以看到运输企业车辆超载等违法行为一旦被纳入信用系统，失信当事人不仅自身贷款、出行受到影响，甚至会影响子女的升学、就业及未来发展。希望所有的运输企业、散户个人都要合规运输。</span></section></section></section></section></section><p></p><p><br/></p>',1,1,7,1600324409,1),(142,'案例三：大货车追尾宝马车！','new-78-427','5f642cbe10887.jpg','案例三：大货车追尾宝马车！','大货车追尾宝马车，事故双方对于处理结果都十分满意！','<p style=\"text-indent:32px\"><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">2020</span><span style=\"font-size:16px;font-family:&#39;微软雅黑&#39;,&#39;sans-serif&#39;\">年<span>8</span>月<span>20</span>日<span>14</span>时<span>09</span>分接到我司参统人报案，称<span>10</span>分钟前，驾驶冀<span>B***82</span>车辆与冀<span>B7***M</span>车辆在天津滨海发生追尾事故，无人员受伤，我司查勘员立即电话指引报案人确保自身安全前提下，拍摄现场照片然后向交警报案，并告知客户已派最近查勘员赶往现场。我司立即委派泛华公估查勘现场，当日下午<span>16</span>时泛华公估查勘员与交警处理完毕，并开具事故认定书我方车辆全责，随后标的车自行开走维修（无车损），三者车开至就近<span>4S</span>店，三者车<span>4S</span>店维修报价<span>140000</span>元，次日我司查勘员由石家庄赶往天津<span>4S</span>店定损，经过一天拆解定损沟通，初步与<span>4S</span>店达成协议<span>115000</span>元，待车辆维修完毕后复勘，并确定最终价格，<span>4S</span>店于<span>9</span>月<span>15</span>日维修完毕，我司复勘完毕后，与<span>4S</span>点确定最终定损金额<span>115000</span>，并于当日打款，开具发票，结案。</span></p><p><img src=\"/Uploads/image/20200918/1600400546739681.jpg\" title=\"1600400546739681.jpg\" _src=\"/Uploads/image/20200918/1600400546739681.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20200918113552.jpg\"/><img src=\"/Uploads/image/20200918/1600400556549773.jpg\" title=\"1600400556549773.jpg\" _src=\"/Uploads/image/20200918/1600400556549773.jpg\" alt=\"微信图片_20200918113601.jpg\"/><img src=\"/Uploads/image/20200918/1600400563922974.jpg\" title=\"1600400563922974.jpg\" _src=\"/Uploads/image/20200918/1600400563922974.jpg\" alt=\"1583377628686266.jpg\"/></p>',170,131,3,1600400574,0),(143,'深圳：普货4米2满载9种危险品   货主和运输公司被罚13万','new-81-938','5f642f7762d68.jpg','深圳：普货4米2满载9种危险品   货主和运输公司被罚13万','8月29日清晨7时30分，执法支队宝安大队在107国道松安检查站开展错时执法对货运车辆进行专项整治。','<p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); text-align: center;\" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"font-size: 24px;\"><strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">深圳：普货4米2满载9种危险品&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 货主和运输公司被罚13万</span></strong></span><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br/></span></p><p style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp;8月29日清晨7时30分，执法支队宝安大队在<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">107国道松安检查站</strong>开展错时执法<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">对货运车辆进行专项整治</strong>。检查过程中，执法人员对车牌号为粤B号牌轻型</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">厢式货车</span><span style=\"letter-spacing: 0.544px; margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 15px; box-sizing: border-box !important; overflow-wrap: break-word !important;\">进行检查。这辆货车看似普普通通，没啥特别之处，但打开车厢一看，执法人员还是被车上装载的各类危化品吓出一身冷汗！</span><br/></p><p style=\"margin-top: 0px; margin-bottom: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; clear: both; min-height: 1em; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></p><p></p><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><img src=\"/Uploads/image/20200918/1600400900825697.png\" title=\"1600400900825697.png\" _src=\"/Uploads/image/20200918/1600400900825697.png\" alt=\"image.png\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 经过清点，这辆货车车厢<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">混装着的危化品种类有氯化铵、氯化镍、氯化亚锡、氢氧化钠、乙酸乙酯、硫氰酸钾、无水亚硫酸钠、四氢呋喃、磷酸。</strong>种类如此繁多，执法人员都快数不过来了，执法人员核对台山市某试剂塑料有限公司的调发清单，与清点核查数量一致。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><img src=\"/Uploads/image/20200918/1600400915709965.png\" title=\"1600400915709965.png\" _src=\"/Uploads/image/20200918/1600400915709965.png\" alt=\"image.png\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">司机马某</span></strong><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br data-filtered=\"filtered\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 我是深圳市某实业有限公司的员工，被公司安排驾驶该车到江门台山市某试剂塑料有限公司，原计划装载该批次货物运输到深圳市光明区公明街道某工业区。但当<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">执法人员要求司机马某出示相关证件时，马某却默默低下了头。</strong></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 经查，该车未取得危险货物道路运输证，<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">所属公司只取得普通道路货物运输许可，未取得道路危险货物运输许可。</strong>于是，执法人员从货物中取样送往检验机构检验，并依法扣押了该车辆。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"2446\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; font-size: 17px; letter-spacing: 0.544px; text-align: justify; white-space: normal; font-family: -apple-system-font, system-ui, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" color:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><section data-tools=\"135编辑器\" data-id=\"2446\" data-color=\"#ef7060\" data-custom=\"#80b135\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-width: 0px; border-style: none; border-color: initial;\"><section style=\"margin: 10px auto; padding: 0px 8px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; border-radius: 3px; border-left: 3px solid rgb(84, 141, 212); border-top-color: rgb(84, 141, 212); border-right-color: rgb(84, 141, 212); border-bottom-color: rgb(84, 141, 212); font-size: 22px; font-weight: inherit; text-align: inherit; text-decoration: inherit;\"><h2 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 20px;\"><strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(77, 168, 238);\">货物均为易燃液体</span></strong></span></h2><h2 style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; font-weight: 400; font-size: 16px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; line-height: 1.75em;\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; color: rgb(77, 168, 238); font-size: 17px;\">运输公司和货主双双被罚</span></h2></section></section></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 随后，宝安大队执法人员对运输公司深圳市某实业有限公司和货主江门台山市某试剂塑料有限公司分别进行了调查取证。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 经过细致调查，执法人员查实江门台山市某试剂塑料有限公司将该批次危险货物交给了未取得危险货物道路运输许可的深圳市某实业有限公司，且深圳市某实业有限公司使用无道路运输证的粤B3号牌车辆进行运输。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 同时，检验机构也如期出具了检验报告，结果所示，该批货物主要成分CH3COOH（乙酸）含量不少于99.5%。<strong style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\">这批货物属于《化学品分类和标签规范》（GB30000.2～30000.29）系列标准的类别3易燃液体。</strong></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><img src=\"/Uploads/image/20200918/1600400935131275.png\" title=\"1600400935131275.png\" _src=\"/Uploads/image/20200918/1600400935131275.png\" alt=\"image.png\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\">&nbsp; &nbsp; &nbsp; 这家试剂公司竟将危化品，交由没有危货运输资质的公司来运输，这种行为不仅对自己不负责任，对客户不负责任，对司机不负责任，更是对沿途的车辆及居民不负责任。针对这种行为，运输公司和货主都要被处罚。</span></section><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" line-height:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><span style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important; font-size: 15px;\"><br style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"/></span></section><section data-support=\"96编辑器\" data-style-id=\"20175\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; color: rgb(51, 51, 51); font-family: -apple-system-font, BlinkMacSystemFont, \" helvetica=\"\" pingfang=\"\" hiragino=\"\" sans=\"\" microsoft=\"\" yahei=\"\" font-size:=\"\" letter-spacing:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" white-space:=\"\" background-color:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; box-sizing: border-box !important; word-wrap: break-word !important;\"><section data-color=\"#ef7060\" style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px; max-width: 100%; letter-spacing: 0.544px; color: rgb(0, 0, 0); font-family: Arial, \" microsoft=\"\" font-size:=\"\" text-align:=\"\" box-sizing:=\"\" border-box=\"\" overflow-wrap:=\"\" break-word=\"\"><section style=\"margin: 0px; padding: 0px 0px 2px; max-width: